		<title>新加坡80%人口已接种疫苗  王乙康：新加坡另一里程碑</title>
		<link>https://atvnewsonline.com/asean/23067/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[甄悦萓]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 29 Aug 2021 04:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
